com.nerjal.json.elements.JsonElement

  • Packages that use JsonElement 
    Package Description
    com.nerjal.json
    This package provides the ability to instantiate and manipulate JSON structures within Java.
    com.nerjal.json.elements
    This package provides all the tools to build and manipulate JSON structures within Java.
    com.nerjal.json.mapper  
    com.nerjal.json.mapper.errors  
    com.nerjal.json.parser
    This package provides all the required tools to properly parse any string or file to JSON and vice-versa.
